{"tid":834200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藝高「熊」膽大 浣熊飛躍10層樓起身即速逃","createTime":"2018-09-24T04:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T04:52:41.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97ca7f8cd6633bdecc8e59f0901a77570e742b68","tid":834200,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180923/_2018092317165818890.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180923%2F_2018092317165818890.jpg&h=7b5e4455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6RDrXPiBxBI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6RDrXPiBxBI&d=TdIywUwWg4I4fsrcBNr70EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=7ae42360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6RDrXPiBxBI</a><br />\n<br />\n美國新澤西州1棟建築物的大廈外牆，日前吸引大批途人駐足，因為有隻浣熊從約10樓高飛身跳下來，摔在地面後竟又立即起身以九秒九秒的速度逃走，圍觀者無不嘩然。<br />\n<br />\n在網上流傳的影片可見，該頭浣熊爬上約10層樓高，突然後腳使力飛躍而下，重重落在地面的沙灘上，接著浣熊在圍觀民眾「Oh My God」的尖叫聲中，起身快速跑走。究竟這頭浣熊有沒有受傷不得而知，可以肯定是牠真的藝高「熊」膽大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/824626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F824626&d=TdIywUwWg4I4fsrcBNr70EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6cfb2aae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F824626&h=f4ff8266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/824626</a>"}]}